Bundled data notices
====================

This package bundles generated dictionary/pitch-accent data derived from 10ten
Japanese Reader snapshot data.

The underlying word dictionary data includes data from JMdict/EDICT.

As stated by 10ten Japanese Reader:

  "This data is the property of the Electronic Dictionary Research and
  Development Group, and is used in conformance with the Group's licence."

Relevant links:

- JMdict/EDICT project:
  https://www.edrdg.org/wiki/index.php/JMdict-EDICT_Dictionary_Project
- EDRDG licence:
  https://www.edrdg.org/edrdg/licence.html


