Generation pipeline
===================

The generated dataset in data/pitch-accent.json is produced by
scripts/build-dataset.ts from:

- vendor/10ten-ja-reader/data/words.ljson

That snapshot is itself generated upstream by 10ten Japanese Reader from data
downloaded from:

- https://data.10ten.life
